originalText.text: We were having some major issues in our family life since our son turned 13 and decided that we should seek out some family counseling. Being located in NYC we had many family counselors to choose from. I am the type to do allot of research before I make up my mind on which direction I am going. I have a friend that is having the same issues with her child and suggested we give Patti a call. So far we have been to 3 sessions and I have seen a big improvement in our family. I would say that anyone in the NYC area that is looking for a good family counselor, that you can try this one out.

originalText.text: After years of troubled times, my wife and I decided that it is time to see a NYC marriage counselor. We have been seeing Patti for about 6 weeks now and I can say that we are doing so much better. If you are looking for marriage counseling nyc I would recommend you to get her a call.
